    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[I]n nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/186">Sicardus</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langubardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, motus
                        Dei omnipotentis misericordia, pro redemptione anime nostre seu gentis et
                        patrię, suggerente potestatis nostre <rs key="#Personal_rank">viro
                            venerabile</rs>
                        <persName key="#Prevosts" ref="#people/192">Bassaci</persName>
                        <rs key="#Prevosts">preposito</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                                ><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> sito
                        infra hanc Beneventana civitate nostra, <rs key="#Intercessory">per
                            rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/1905"
                            >Roffrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">referendarii</rs> nostri, concedimus in
                        prephato Beate Sophie cenobio, ubi <persName key="#Abbesses"
                            ref="#people/3461">Wilerone</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatissa</rs> preesse videtur, ipse <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terre</rs> in <placeName ref="#places/605"
                            key="#Geographic_regions #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property"
                            >Legurie</placeName> que empte habent <rs key="#Cartula #Venditio">per
                            cartula</rs> ipsi <rs key="#Slave">servi</rs> prephati <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> de loco Ferusuanu da ipsi <rs
                            key="#Royal_slave">servi sacri nostri palatii</rs> qui habitatori sunt
                        in Mairconu et alii sunt habitatori a Noce et alii ubi a Silba nominatur, in
                        integrum ipsa terra sicut ipsorum cartula continetur per singula loca in
                        eodem monasterio ipso concessimus, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et
                        deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum cunta que prelegitur ipsi servi
                        et eorum heredes habere et possidere valeat sicut cartula illorum continunt
                        et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldis vel a
                        quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis
                        temporibus possideatis. Quod vero pręceptus concessionis ex iussionis
                        nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Writer" ref="#people/3462"
                            >Theodericus</persName>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> secundo anno, mense aprilis,
                        duodecima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
